Scatter Plots of mtcars
===============================================================

```{r, echo = FALSE}
ggplot(mtcars,aes(x = wt, y=mpg, col= factor(cyl))) +
        geom_point(size = 1.5) +
        geom_smooth(method = lm, se = TRUE, color = "black") +
        labs(title = "mpg vs. wt")
```

